### A-4-6b. 訓練 Regression：CNN（PyTorch 1D-CNN，epochs=30）
# 回傳: { "training_job_id": "...", "status": "running" }
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modeling/train
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "{{regFileId}}",
  "preprocessing_id": "{{regPrepId1}}",
  "task_category": "regression",
  "models": {
    "CNN": {
      "enabled": true,
      "params": {"epochs": 30, "batch_size": 16, "learning_rate": 0.001}
    }
  },
  "hyperparameter_tuning": {
    "grid_search": false,
    "k_fold": 5
  }
}

###
@regCnnJobId = 69f08ce441fc90e81c604376
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modeling/status/{{regCnnJobId}}


### A-4-6c. 訓練 Regression：LinearRegression（OLS 線性回歸）
# 與其他模型走同一 flow，只是換 models 的 key。
# 可調參數: fit_intercept(bool), positive(bool)
# 回傳: { "training_job_id": "...", "status": "running" }
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modeling/train
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "{{regFileId}}",
  "preprocessing_id": "{{regPrepId1}}",
  "task_category": "regression",
  "models": {
    "LinearRegression": {
      "enabled": true,
      "params": {"fit_intercept": true, "positive": false}
    }
  },
  "hyperparameter_tuning": {
    "grid_search": false,
    "k_fold": 5
  }
}

###
@regLinearJobId = <貼上回傳的 training_job_id>
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modeling/status/{{regLinearJobId}}

### A-4-6d. 訓練 Regression：LSTM（PyTorch 序列型，將曲線視為時間序列）
# 同一 flow；LSTM 對「隨進度/時間變化」的曲線型資料特別合適。
# 可調參數: hidden_size, num_layers, epochs, batch_size, learning_rate
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modeling/train
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "{{regFileId}}",
  "preprocessing_id": "{{regPrepId1}}",
  "task_category": "regression",
  "models": {
    "LSTM": {
      "enabled": true,
      "params": {
        "hidden_size": 32,
        "num_layers": 1,
        "epochs": 50,
        "batch_size": 16,
        "learning_rate": 0.001
      }
    }
  },
  "hyperparameter_tuning": {
    "grid_search": false,
    "k_fold": 5
  }
}

###
@regLstmJobId = <貼上回傳的 training_job_id>
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modeling/status/{{regLstmJobId}}

### A-4-6e. 訓練 Regression：一次比較多模型（PLS + LinearRegression + LSTM 同任務）
# 前台若要在同一份資料上並排比較線性與序列模型，一個請求即可。
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modeling/train
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "{{regFileId}}",
  "preprocessing_id": "{{regPrepId1}}",
  "task_category": "regression",
  "models": {
    "PLS": {
      "enabled": true,
      "params": {"n_components": 7}
    },
    "LinearRegression": {
      "enabled": true,
      "params": {"fit_intercept": true, "positive": false}
    },
    "LSTM": {
      "enabled": true,
      "params": {"hidden_size": 32, "num_layers": 1, "epochs": 50, "batch_size": 16, "learning_rate": 0.001}
    }
  },
  "hyperparameter_tuning": {
    "grid_search": false,
    "k_fold": 5
  }
}

###
@regMultiJobId = <貼上回傳的 training_job_id>
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modeling/status/{{regMultiJobId}}


