### B-3-1. 執行前處理：SNV，component=Class（分類目標建議固定使用 Class）
# 回傳: { "preprocessing_id": "...", "status": "running" }
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/preprocessing/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "{{clsFileId}}",
  "component": "Class",
  "methods": {
    "snv": true,
    "sg": null,
    "derivative": null,
    "normalization": null,
    "wavelength_selection": null
  }
}

