@clsPrepId1 = 69eb1c15f5e807e63305de05

### B-3-2. 查詢分類前處理狀態
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/preprocessing/status/{{clsPrepId1}}

### B-3-3. 取得分類前處理結果
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/preprocessing/{{clsPrepId1}}

### B-3-4. 執行前處理：SNV + SG，Class
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/preprocessing/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "{{clsFileId}}",
  "component": "Class",
  "methods": {
    "snv": true,
    "sg": {
      "window_size": 11,
      "polynomial_order": 2
    },
    "derivative": null,
    "normalization": null,
    "wavelength_selection": null
  }
}

###
@clsPrepId2 = 69eb1c15f5e807e63305de05

### B-3-5. 查詢 Label 前處理狀態
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/preprocessing/status/{{clsPrepId2}}

### B-3-6. 執行前處理：SNV + 一階微分 + 波長選擇(RF_Feature_Importance)，Class
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/preprocessing/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "{{clsFileId}}",
  "component": "Class",
  "methods": {
